name: Talomophora Goose
description:
--Fig03--
Talomophora Goose is Branchipoda Ave creature from Kepler 20, and exoplanet located 948 light years away from Earth, in the constellation of Lyra.
Talomophora lives and floats both in skies of Helium and Neon, where it swarms in trillions of individuals.
They are the size of an average human hand, but can build both steel and rock structures, since they work in enormous groups.
The species’ individuals are very playful and lovely beings. They spend most of their life playing, having an infinite number of games they play with the whole swarm.
